OL,3,CCampaigners head to Westminster to
OL,4,Cchampion black maternal mental health
OL,6,FA group of mothers and campaigners
OL,7,Fhave met with MPs at Westminster to
OL,8,Fhighlight the challenges facing black
OL,9,Fwomen during and after pregnancy.
OL,11,FThe Motherhood Group said its Black
OL,12,FMaternal Mental Health Report is the
OL,13,Ffirst of its kind in the UK - drawing
OL,14,Fon the experiences of more than 18,000
OL,15,Fblack mothers.
OL,17,FAccording to the report, black mothers
OL,18,Fare more than twice as likely to be
OL,19,Fhospitalised with mental illness in
OL,20,Fthe weeks before and after birth.
