OL,3,CCampaigners head to Westminster to
OL,4,Cchampion black maternal mental health
OL,6,FHowever, many of those affected avoid
OL,7,Fseeking support due to stigma and fear
OL,8,Fof social services, the report found.
OL,10,FThe survey also found that issues such
OL,11,Fas depression, trauma, and anxiety can
OL,12,Fbe directly fueled by experiences of
OL,13,Fracism, stereotyping, and
OL,14,Fmicroaggressions in NHS maternity care.
OL,16,FThose who shared their experiences
OL,17,Foften described feeling "unheard",
OL,18,F"dismissed", and "judged" and the
OL,19,Freport also found there to be a lack
OL,20,Fof culturally safe spaces for black
OL,21,Fmothers in the NHS.
