OL,3,CCampaigners head to Westminster to
OL,4,Cchampion black maternal mental health
OL,6,FFounder and chief executive The
OL,7,FMotherhood Group Sandra Igwe said the
OL,8,Fresearch was conducted over nine and a
OL,9,Fhalf years of engagements, workshops,
OL,10,Ffocus groups.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday Ms Igwe and her team
OL,13,Fpresented their findings in Parliament
OL,14,Fto politicians, healthcare
OL,15,Fpractitioners and community
OL,16,Forganisations.
