OL,6,FShe told ITV News London: "That, for
OL,7,Fus was wonderful, bringing together
OL,8,Fall different types of people to focus
OL,9,Fon the needs, the unique and
OL,10,Findividual needs that black mothers
OL,11,Fneed in the perinatal mental health
OL,12,Fpathway."
OL,14,FMs Igwe said she is "extremely
OL,15,Fconfident" that their report will
OL,16,Fbring about change.
