OL,3,CCampaigners head to Westminster to
OL,4,Cchampion black maternal mental health
OL,6,FShe added: "It doesn't just highlight
OL,7,Fthe issues and the problems, it looks
OL,8,Fat the solutions and recommendations
OL,9,Ffor improvement and it looks at also
OL,10,Fthe ways that we want to receive care.
OL,12,F"For far too long, black mothers have
OL,13,Fbeen spoken about, but never have been
OL,14,Fbrought to the table. But today we
OL,15,Fcreated our own table in Parliament."
OL,17,FOne of the mothers speaking in
OL,18,FWestminster on Tuesday was Natalie
OL,19,FThanni, who said she felt she was not
OL,20,Flistened to during the birth of her
OL,21,Fson.
