OL,6,FHaving suffered a placental abruption
OL,7,Fand a haemorrhage, she lost two litres
OL,8,Fof blood in four minutes and nearly
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FMs Thanni ended up having to have a
OL,12,Fserious emergency Caesarean section
OL,13,Fand went on to experience postpartum
OL,14,Fdepression.
OL,16,F"I got called delusional by a
OL,17,Fmidwife," she said, adding: "I also
OL,18,Fgot told that every pregnancy is
OL,19,Fdifferent and I should get out my
OL,20,Fmind."
