OL,6,FMs Thanni went on: "Originally, I
OL,7,Fdidn't want to speak about it ... but
OL,8,Fthen, as a mother of girls, I don't
OL,9,Fwant anybody to go through what I went
OL,10,Fthrough.
OL,12,F"I just kept on fighting, I kept on
OL,13,Fasking, I want to speak to somebody
OL,14,Felse, another opinion, another
OL,15,Fopinion, until I finally got listened
OL,16,Fto. But not all mums are the same.
OL,18,F"Not all mums will keep on speaking up
OL,19,Fover and over again".
